name: astroship-pro
title: Astroship Pro
desc: Astroship Pro is a SAAS, Startup Astro Website Template and Landing Page built with Astro & Tailwind CSS.
article:
Astroship Pro is a pro version of the popular starter template Astroship. Astroship Pro template can be used for SAAS, startups, marketing websites & landing pages. Built with Astro & TailwindCSS. You can quickly create any website with this website template.

Features:

  • Pro Layouts & Features
  • 10+ Pages Included
  • Blog with Pagination Support
  • Pricing with Comparison
  • Features & Integrations Page
  • Responsive Navbar with Dropdown
  • Working Contact form
  • About & Team Page

Check out the Free Version here.
